locality: Itremo massif, W of Ambatofinandrahana. Along road to Col d'Itremo, ca. 2 km before (NE of) bridge over Ambalarangolana creek. Open marble-quartzite slope to W of road. Collected with G.E. Schatz, T. Andriamihajarivo, C. Hong-Wa, S. Rapanarivo & H. Rabarison.
Madagascar. Prov. Fianarantsoa. c. 35 km S of Ambositra.
